Membership at The Bluffs
The Bluffs Golf Course
offers various types of memberships, whether you are a full-time resident of the area or just down for the winter season, or maybe you just want to play in the summer months.  The Bluffs can also offer corporate memberships.
Any Membership may make a reservation up to 14 days in advance. Some restrictions apply. Annual Memberships will start on November 1.
Range Balls included in membership.
Any Membership is entitled to a 10% discount for any pro shop merchandise.
All Prices include 7% Sales Tax
